title: Nauman joins Moss & Barnett’s multifamily agency lending team
text:
Home / Brief / Nauman joins Moss & Barnett’s multifamily agency lending team Nauman joins Moss & Barnett’s multifamily agency lending team By: Hank Long Hank Long October 9, 2015 5:04 pm 0 Jeremy J. Nauman (submitted photo) 
The Minneapolis-based Moss & Barnett law firm recently hired attorney Jeremy J. Nauman to work in its national multifamily agency lending practice group. Nauman received his J.D., cum laude, from Northern Illinois University College of 
Law and his B.A., cum laude, from Winona State University. 
The firm is located in downtown Minneapolis and features 75-plus attorneys and paralegals representing clients as advisers and advocates. Share this:
